{"tid":479110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲會有人覺得讀大學好輕鬆？","createTime":"2017-11-24T17:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T03:08:33.000Z","uid":116503,"like":38,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d1366744f5f46e0d473f8209e3d7d91f1ad686d8","tid":479110,"uid":116503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:30:13.000Z","msg":"一同人講自己讀書好辛苦 就會俾人話廢 無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實讀u真係好撚痛苦 自問自己唔係特別叻 都係死溫爛溫先碌到個ugc degree  全家上下都對自己期望勁高 想quit u都唔敢講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  宜家日日返學上堂都唔知做緊乜 好難focus 好似聽極都唔入耳 gpa從來都無同屋企人講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉 讀到咁 仲有兩年點挨啊<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n可能真係我廢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9a67f4164959fa433a72d5a2ba93f92f1003f4","tid":479110,"uid":135710,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:33:08.000Z","msg":"Year1表示已經想quit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4f9c053a3c7eeb6b76370603094f68a079052a","tid":479110,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:34:23.000Z","msg":"首先 屋企人無能力理解嘅話 你應酬下佢地得 唔使同佢地商議酙酌交代太多<br />\n第二 你可以試下搵大學輔導／臨床心理學家／academic advisor<br />\n第三 有啲人有家底唔care 個hon咪輕鬆囉 你做好自己本分就得 唔使理人"},{"pid":"edc280f09acd1c4df78772bcc6720e757bb7b21f","tid":479110,"uid":116503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Year1表示已經想quit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一直由year 1到依家都成日唸quit"},{"pid":"db371ea6867cd762fb6e9719957ec572e1693cc9","tid":479110,"uid":116503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:50:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先 屋企人無能力理解嘅話 你應酬下佢地得 唔使同佢地商議酙酌交代太多<br />\n第二 你可以試下搵大學輔導／臨床心理學家／academic advisor<br />\n第三 <span style=\"color: red;\">有啲人有家底唔care</span> 個hon咪輕鬆囉 你做好自己本分就得 唔使理人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贏在起跑線真係無咩包袱"},{"pid":"e2ea40bae819bbdc6a2a95b0817d59d1509929dc","tid":479110,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:52:42.000Z","msg":"其實又真係幾輕鬆<br />\n<br />\n只係由班老鬼講出黎果時，你開初都唔明點解條撚樣盲字都唔識多個，都夠膽死可以用居高臨下既語氣潤你讀書輕鬆<br />\n<br />\n但你想串佢小學都未畢業就收皮唔好出聲獻醜啦屌你老母果時，你又諗起佢一早已經霸佔社會資源做緊你老細，你連開口屌返佢既資格，都好似無左<br />\n<br />\n好唔順氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835d371447aa69de760b0718e025f1d0a1a14757","tid":479110,"uid":53254,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:53:45.000Z","msg":"係，你當磨練自己<br />\n<br />\n讀書厭力再大，都係自己食屎<br />\n做野壓力係大在，成村人睇住你食屎，甚至成team食屎<br />\n<br />\n始終你都要學識面對"},{"pid":"1e933937469fd264f0e888f15f666d2e0889ad81","tid":479110,"uid":57962,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:55:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e52da172770c6859691f112069ac4febdf8889e","tid":479110,"uid":51978,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:56:01.000Z","msg":"不過講返啲歷史緣由<br />\n舊時讀大學啲人真係唔使讀書<br />\n因爲以前香港跟英式學制 平時唔係成日有assignments/assessment<br />\n係一年先考一次試 所以以前港大住hall啲人先可以打波打到天昏地暗<br />\n後來跟美式學制先有gpa 呢家嘢"},{"pid":"014aa9cd6a5d3fc342623ffceb254f64186b2bee","tid":479110,"uid":102700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:56:28.000Z","msg":"唔求first hon咪輕鬆"},{"pid":"3771cd2c0cc0fd159ea22090067de898e392c64e","tid":479110,"uid":157304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:59:20.000Z","msg":"換個心態，求合格咪算囉"},{"pid":"84ecf94cd8659700ad587c12a5528700f58e59e5","tid":479110,"uid":116503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T18:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔求first hon咪輕鬆</blockquote><br />\n直情想cut hon添啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/no